: \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lottie_Dod\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lottie_Dod\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While I am devastated, it's the right decision to make as all any of us want at the end of the day is a happy healthy horse.\", \"from\": 1991, \"to\": 2115, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We will have to keep the show jumping phase a secret from Lottie as she would not be impressed if she thought she was missing one of her favourite phases.\\\"\", \"from\": 2117, \"to\": 2273, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2176, \"end\": 2182, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lottie_Dod\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 3.2911913554817634e-13, \"text\": \"Lottie\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lottie_Dod\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lottie_Dod\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sarah and Action Lady M will be replaced in the Irish team for the final phase by London 2012 Olympian Aoife Clark and Sportsfield Freelance.\", \"from\": 2275, \"to\": 2416, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2275, \"end\": 2280, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Jane_Smith\", \"score\": 0.9934820879543695, \"rank\": 0.006386020206946613, \"text\": \"Sarah\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Jane_Smith\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Jane_Smith\"}, {\"begin\": 2323, \"end\": 2328, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999905410601858, \"rank\": 4.101252598677474e-06, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 2364, \"end\": 2377, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.632510316196903e-13, \"text\": \"2012 Olympian\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://d